results.name: Let F(x) = 1 + 1*x + 4*x^2 + 10*x^3 + ..., the g.f. for A000293 (solid partitions), and write F(x) = 1/Product_{n>=1} E(n)^a(n) where E(n) = Product_{k>=n} (1 - x^(n*k)).
results.author: _Joerg Arndt_, Aug 03 2011
